                        <H3 style="font-style: underline">3. <u>Follow the "Control Chart": 


                        
                        </u>
                        </H3>

                        <p style="padding: 0px 0px 3% 0px;font-size: 23px;color: black; font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif,';">
                            The control chart involves listing down things that you can change and control and those that lie outside your control scope. Whenever you find yourself overthinking, draw this chart and focus your attention solely on those aspects that are under your control. For example, while preparing for an exam, you could draw a control chart as provided below:
  </p>


