                        </p>
 <br>
                        <H3 style=" font-style: underline">6. <u>Divert your Thoughts: 


                        </u>
                        </H3>

                        <p style="padding: 0px 0px 3% 0px;font-size: 23px;color: black; font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif,';">
                            Diverting your thoughts by distracting your mind to another task is a good coping strategy to channelise your energy to do something interesting. You can do this by exercising or jogging outside, cooking up a delicious meal, painting, listening to music or following your hobbies. This will shift your concentration on the task at hand, leaving you little time to worry and overthink.
  </p>

